property.description:
District 10
Rare elevated 2.5 level Bungalow House right at the fringe of Orchard road
Sited at Chatsworth Park Good Class Bungalow Area
Car porch level: Can park at least 6 cars, BBQ area, Gym room with toilet, Garage area, Maid room with toilet

- Prestigious location. Walking distance to Sixth Avenue MRT. Near many reputable schools.
- Luxurious space. Wide frontage in a quiet neighbourhood.
- With internal lift and outdoor swimming pool
- Bright, airy and spacious with high ceilings
- Spacious 5 bedrooms with en-suite bathrooms + maids room.
- Master bedroom, junior master bedroom and 2 common room (all with en-suite bathrooms).
- basement: large entertainment area (TV Room) + home shelter, storeroom and powder room.

This pair of brand new 3.5sty f'hold Shelford bungalow is all about spaciousness
 with more than 11,000sf. Ideally located in the Bukit Timah landed housing 
enclave. This contemporary modern pair softly assimilate into the landscape amongst other 
neighbouring landed properties. The detail orientated homes were designed to imbue modernism and timelessness.

Quiet indulgence, the architectural language generate spaces that seamlessly integrate modern living and 
entertainment in the 21st century. A great home for multi-tier generation. Near top schools like NYPS, RGPS

Newly renovated F'hold 2.5sty bungalow land approx 4700sf built up approx 
5000sf, with 5+1 cosy bedrooms. Tucked in the swanky prime Bukit Timah precinct. Close to an 
array of amenities & good schools like Nanyang Girls', Raffles Girl's Primary, Hwa Chong, 
NYPS. Easy connectivity to major expressways. Short drive to Orchard Road.
